data.description: For the discerning buyer, we present a GORGEOUS,  CUSTOM-BUILT home showcasing SUPERB QUALITY & CRAFTSMANSHIP! Boasting 2x6 studding, 2 x 12 flr joists, 12-in poured concrete walls w/2- x 1-ft footer and mostly Plaster walls!  All set on a .76 -acre, level, corner lot!  Even the outdoor space is REMARKABLE w/a sun-drenched deck, significant covered patio, dimensional waterfall and vibrant landscaping! If you love to entertain, you want to see this! Come. Join me inside where the main level presents both a Family Room and Formal Living Rm;  an Eat-In-Kitchen w/40 feet of solid Cherry, upgraded cabinets and Corian countertops, a formal Dining Rm, Sunroom, Laundry/Mud Rm, Workshop & 2-stall Garage! Upstairs is an Office/Den, Guest Bath and 2 BRs in addition to a colossal Owner's En-Suite Bath, Sauna & Bonus area for your Peloton Bike!  NOTEWORTHY: 6-panel Oak doors/trim, Anderson windows, 7-zone heat + more! The workshop can be converted to a 3rd stall!  Come see what QUALITY looks like!
